<template>
  <v-container>
    <v-row>
      <v-col sm="4" class="pa-3" v-for="product in products" :key="product._id">
        <v-card class="pa-1">
          <v-img height="250" :src="`/${product.image}`"></v-img>
        </v-card
      >
      <v-card-title></v-card-title>
    </v-col>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
import API from "../api";
export default {
  name: "Home",
  data() {
    return {
      products: [],
    };
  },
  async create() {
    this.products = await API.getAllProduct();
  },
};
</script>
